# Storage Directory

This directory contains SQLite database files for the application.

## Files
- `development.sqlite3` - Development database (gitignored)
- `test.sqlite3` - Test database (gitignored)
- `demo.sqlite3` - Demo database with sample data (gitignored)
- `production.sqlite3` - Production database (gitignored)

All database files are excluded from version control for privacy and security.